data.description: Offer accepted - accepting backup offers! Updated and fully fenced, this 3 bedroom home is on an oversized corner lot with mature trees, solid hardwood floors and stainless steel appliances with a garage + storage and plenty of parking and no HOA! This home has a long private driveway, a garage with a new roof, and additional storage space with a separate access door! Centrally located on a quiet street just blocks from UNC, shopping and with quick access to HWY 85! Thoughtfully maintained, and freshly painted, this charming home is move-in ready! Brandon List at Tru RATE Mortgage is offering a 2% preferred lender incentive based on loan amount for qualified buyers so schedule your showing and get qualified today! We hope to see you there!
